body:
#### PR description:

Remove legacy CUDA pixel local reconstruction:
  - Remove legacy CUDA beamspot modules and data formats;
  - Remove legacy CUDA pixel rechits modules and data formats;
  - Remove legacy CUDA pixel clustering modules and data formats;
  - Remove legacy CUDA pixel seeding modules;
  - Remove legacy CUDA pixel digi converter modules and data formats;
  - Remove CUDA-related code from the legacy pixel converter and the `PixelCPEFast`
  - Convert remaining uses to `pixelClustering` constants and `SiPixelHitStatus` data formats.

A separate PR will add back an alpaka version of the pixel clustering tests.

#### PR validation:

Matrix tests pass.
